name: Robot Metropolis Carnival Series 8/10
description: The Robot Metropolis Carnival. The focused mouse developed cunning upon the discovery that a ticket booth is an absolute necessity if revenue is to be made. With the support of the rest of the carnival population this booth was crafted. The crazed robot found scraps of material to craft the structure. The crazed clown kept everyone moving. The dazed child helped with the ticket printing and currency receiving mechanisms. Nobody remembers what the fluffy dog was doing, but all remember it was there.
